INSERT INTO lamport_counter (id, current_value, last_updated)

          ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
            SET current_value = lamport_counter.current_value + 1, last_updated = now()
          RETURNING id, current_value as "currentValue", last_updated as "lastUpdated";
